entries.femaleVariant: [Sit down] Let's wait here.
[Get up] I think he likes me.
Black Thorton Merrimac. In the street, three minutes, front seat.
A mutual friend.
Don't turn around. Eyes on the court.
Who sent you?
No tail.
Were you followed? Did you even bother to check?
Not a talker, huh? Too bad – 'cause I need answers.
Honestly? Not sure.
I'm not sloppy.
Heh. Your silence says it all.
Doubt I was tailed.
Dunno. Wasn't lookin' for a tail.
Take me for a fuckin' gonk? An amateur?
So you didn't check.
Interrogation over?
After you.
Black Thorton.
Ehh...
Johnny...? Who the hell's breathin' down my neck?
How the fuck should I know? Only see what you see.
Hands. What you holdin'?
[Show hands] Got a token.
[Turn around] You first.
Can you see him?
I see you holdin' something. Show me.
Got this token. Mean anything to you?
After you.
It does. But I need to make sure.
Nope, nuh-uh.
Don't do that, just don't.
Don't know who I'm talkin' to.
Like to know who I'm talkin' to.
Old line, there, choom.
You know who I am. Now hands, show me.
Fuck your interrogations.
Don't know you, don't work for you, so you can fuck off with the interrogation bullshit.
Ugh…!
A mutual friend.
We don't have mutual friends.
Rosalind--
I don't know any Rosalind.
And neither do you.
Interrogation? We're just talkin'…
[Turn around] This is stupid.
Well, you get one point for being candid.
Is she safe?
You sure fooled me.
Let me ask you again – who sent you?
Ah, so you'd rather do the hard way.
Hope so.
Not if we waste any more time.
Last time I saw 'er she was. Can only hope that's still the case.
Hard to say, the longer we sit here.
No, fuck this. Ain't talkin' this way.
Wrong move.
Attagirl.
[Get up] What a psycho.
What a fuckin' wacko.
I think we really hit it off.
Like him already. Let's scoot.
Sure, bet he's got candy in that van. Ready to find out?
But fine, that'll have to do.
Rosalind Myers.
Friend survived an accident. Ya might've heard.
I might've.
That's it, dribble around 'im.
Right...
Reed...?
That it? Interrogation over?
We better leave separately… Don't want anyone to get suspicious. You first.
Slippery motherfucker…
Dunno, man. The fuck Hansen got against a plane? Had a bad day 'n' wham, shoot that shit down?
Never know with that mofo. 'Member them badges he strung up the last time he was pissed?
With the right gams installed, man, a three-point dunk ain't even hard.
Game needs some damn rule changes.
Vance's elbow has a hitch. Dude needs an upgrade.
Think it'll hitch today?
Oh, not a doubt in my mind it'll hitch.
M-mm, not today, choom. Dogtown's locked down tight.
Last chance 'fore I hand it off. 'Sides, there's way-wide gaps in security…
Yeah, no, I ain't dyin' today. Thanks but no thanks. Now leave me the fuck alone.
Where were you when it crashed?
On the Net. Traffic blew up like crazy, almost made my ice bath boil.
What's the word? Was it really the NUSA?
Pfff... I don't know. It was chaos on there, choomba.
Yeah, yeah... as crazy as it is out here…
A piece of the plane smashed into our kitchen, you believe that?
Whaaat? Everybody OK?
Better. My input loves it. He always said we could use another window.
Gonna take Jayden for the next gig.
Why him? He a weak-ass pussy.
Yeah, but he's kinda hot… but no, thing is, he got some nova supplements off Ronald.
I asked you a question. Is she safe?
Zone defense, that. Keep pushin'.
Got a pro spy here, V…
Already? Was startin' to have fun…
Don’t wanna be caught holdin' hands?
Right...
Look out!
Keep it cool, V.
Keeps his cards close, this one.
Gonna be a game to remember.
Johnny Silverhand... basketball fan? That's new.
You know what I mean.
Nother game's starting. One where your head's the fuckin' ball.
You don't trust Myers.
You're exaggerating.
Just come out and say it – you don't trust Myers.
Know her type is all.
Politicians?
Worse. Armed Forces.
Sayin' "no" to high-ranking cunts 's like puttin' your mouth over the barrel of their gun. Gets shitty fast if you try to run.
Sure you're not overreacting?
Whatever. Ain't me goin' off to war.
War? C'mon, that's a stretch.
Tell me.
Really wanna do this now?
Every grunt gets a rifle, flak jacket and a bunch of promises. Comes a time you're outta ammo, Kevlar's® tattered cardboard and what's left of the promises…?
Maybe not the kind of war you're imaginin', but it's war all right.
FIA, NUSA, Arasaka – same shit, different packaging. Hope you're hungry, soldier, 'cause you're about to chow down.
Fuck-all, I'm guessin'.
Exactly. And that's when they reach for the stick they call "values."
Gettin' shelled in your dugout, chooms're takin' refreshing phosphorous showers, and some officer's rantin' 'bout loyalty and duty.
Still wrestling with demons?
Understood. Won't get dragged into anything.
Sounds like you got some shit to work through.
Get what I'm tryin' to tell you?
Gotta face your demons sometime, Johnny.
Didn't actually have a problem with 'em - till now.
Think you're forgetting somethin' – I never took that oath.
And rightly fuckin' so. 'S bad enough we're on their payroll.
I'll keep one foot out the door, OK?
Silverhand the Brave – a deserter?!
Never told me you deserted.
Never told me about that.
Nothin' to be proud of.
Tore out that chapter, crumpled it, swallowed it. Our sitch hairballed it back up.
Politicians, military 'runners, intelligence operatives... and Colonel Hansen for dessert.
All the rotten fish in one fuckin' barrel, this Dogtown.
Gonna hold you to that.
Understood. Won't get dragged into anything.
Got the warning. I'll keep one foot out the door.
Too late. Swore an oath to the New fuckin' United fuckin' States of America.
If you faked it, it makes you a pushover.
If you meant it, it makes you a tool.
Supposed to trust deserters now?
Trustin' a deserter… kinda contradictory, don'tcha think?
Hey, tryin' to tell you somethin' important.
The dauntless Johnny Silverhand, scourge of megacorps...
Gonk who enlisted was Robert John Linder. Got roped in with easy cash, promise of fame, glory.
If you're gonna book outta the army, ya gotta be honest, admit you made a mistake.
Linder snuffed it. Was a different kid who crawled home from the front.
One thing I did learn, caked in blood and mud…
Uh, no offense, but... could we just chill a sec? Watch the game some, enjoy just that?
entries.maleVariant: No offense, but... could we just chill a sec? Watch the game some, enjoy just that?

entries.femaleVariant: What, don't believe me?
Could enjoy the game instead.
What was that?
Now, Johnny? Really feel a need to get this off your chest?
Why not? How 'bout a hotdog and a cold beer while we're at it? Pretend we don't got a worry in the world.
That would be so nice…
Well, when you put it like that... fine…
Savor it while it lasts...
Get comfy. Gonna twist your ears, lay some wisdom on ya.
After every carrot comes the stick. Allow me to illustrate.
The moment you stop shittin' carrots and they wave the values stick – fuckin' run, rabbit. Run.
You even listenin'?
Desertion as bravery... now that's Johnnyspeak if I ever heard it.
Maybe a little. Sue me.
And that, dare I say it, takes fuckin' guts.
Take it from a deserter.
Here we go…
Vanquisher of hypocrisy, bolted from the army? Give this man his fucking encore!
Johnny, I... I didn't mean to--
'S OK. Was a long time ago.
Ronnie?! Shit, say goodbye to that pretty face.
Thought the same thing. Somethin' nasty's brewin'...
How do ya mean?
You're up against seasoned players, whereas you… just stumbled onto the court.
So go out and play. Just don't get played.
Metaphor gettin' through or not?
Fuckin' storm's what's brewin' Don't let the sunshine fool ya.
Take it from a deserter.
These're trained sociopaths. Pretend to be your friends while they fuckin' ain't.
I see you still got a ways to go. We'll work with what we got.
You see the guy I was talking to?
Hey, y'see the guy I was talkin' to millisec ago?
Big guy? Coat lookin' like he's plannin' on flashin' some kids, hah!
Hey, shut it or get lost.
Hm. Something's up, for sure.
Cut the riddles, please.
So then…
We were saying…?
Friend here passed out. Too much excitement.
Told me about that already.
Remember you sayin' you deserted. There more to the story?
Ah, just another life lesson you could fuckin' use.
[Throw ball] Game on!
V on the court, baby. Check this out!
[Sure throw] Let's see if I still got it.
See if I still got the ol' moves…
Aaaah! And the crowd goes wild… for a fuckin' refund.
Nice! Might not get your ass handed to ya after all.
Yo, what the shit?!
Who? Oh, them plainclothes pigs? Good call, if you askin' me.
Right, so musta had a reason to shoot down the prez, too. Meanin', if he did.
Pretty sure the choom said daytime… Only thing we're meetin' here's a stray bullet, V.
Best seats in the house.
Best seats in the house.
Any idea what triggered Hansen?
So whaddya think crawled up Hansen's ass? Offiin' the Prez's no joke.
Weren't here, were ya? Seven years ago? When the bitch started droppin' bombs? No? Fuck you.
Nah, it's no joke, choom. It's justice for the past. Like you'd know anythin' about it.
It always so peaceful here?
First time in the area. It always so… calm around here?
Calm... ? Heheh… Hmph. Guess you chose the right day, holmes. Peeps're usually packin' iron, ready to jump.
But watch yourself after dark, yeah? New faces attract attention. The bad kind, feel me?
